metadata.name: The Maiden
metadata.description:
“When in love or inspired, an eternal kiss from the divine awaits us all.”

Drawing inspiration from mysticism, ancient cultures, and the dualism of self, this series explores uneasy scenes where black predominates over all colours. Deep contrasts serve as a reminder that beauty exists in both the dark & the light, as two halves of the same whole. 

Each piece uses a blend of both traditional art and AI to create a dream-like landscape, exquisitely detailed at 8k resolution.
